snippet.title: Botany Manor - Announcement Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Botany Manor is coming to Nintendo Switch next year! Wishlist today: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/botany-manor-switch/

Welcome to Botany Manor, a stately home in 19th century England. You play as its inhabitant Arabella Greene, a retired botanist. Explore your house and gardens, filled with research, to figure out the ideal habitat for a collection of forgotten flora. Grow each plant to discover the mysterious qualities they hold…

#BotanyManor #IndieWorld #NintendoSwitch
